      "message": "Patch Set 9:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/65e9246c-7a94-11e2-b916-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
